  "prompt": "Build a Todo application with the following features:\n\n1. **Add todos**: Input field + button to add new todos\n2. **Complete todos**: Click to toggle completion state (strikethrough)\n3. **Delete todos**: Remove button for each todo\n4. **Filter todos**: Buttons to show All / Active / Completed\n5. **Persist to localStorage**: Todos survive page refresh\n6. **Clear completed**: Button to remove all completed todos\n7. **Todo count**: Show \"X items left\" for active todos\n\nUse vanilla JavaScript, no frameworks. Render to the #app div.",

